Class Unit

  • java.lang.Object
    • Unit

  • public class Unit
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a piece on the board. This piece could be known, theoretical, or even owned by a Lake. (Not Joking, lakes actually own pieces) Created by Steven Bruman on 1/30/2018. Edited by Steven Bruman and William Jacobs Version 4/18/2018

    • Constructor Summary
